                            <comment id="14119090" author="daijy" created="Wed, 3 Sep 2014 01:57:52 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4146&quot; title=&quot;Create a target to run mr and tez unit test in one shot&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4146&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-4146&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-1.patch has one problem. If test-mr fail, ant does not run test-tez. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4146&quot; title=&quot;Create a target to run mr and tez unit test in one shot&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4146&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-4146&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-2.patch fix the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14120521" author="cheolsoo" created="Wed, 3 Sep 2014 22:44:24 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I think this is a typo. &quot;test-smoke.failed&quot; should be &quot;test-tez.failed&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
     &amp;lt;target name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test-tez&quot;&lt;/span&gt; depends=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;setTezEnv,setWindowsPath,setLinuxPath,compile-test,jar,debugger.check,jackson-pig-3039-test-download&quot;&lt;/span&gt; description=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Run tez unit tests&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
-        &amp;lt;macro-test-runner test.file=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${test.tez.file}&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
+        &amp;lt;macro-test-runner test.file=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${test.tez.file}&quot;&lt;/span&gt; tests.failed=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test-smoke.failed&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
+        &amp;lt;fail &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test-smoke.failed&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;Tests failed!&amp;lt;/fail&amp;gt;
     &amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Otherwise, looks good to me. +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14120719" author="daijy" created="Thu, 4 Sep 2014 00:58:31 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix typo.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14120720" author="daijy" created="Thu, 4 Sep 2014 00:59:03 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch committed to trunk. Thanks Cheolsoo for review!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
